<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="讀誦" xml:id="gsz0870c09shiDaoXian"><lb
ed="T" n="0870c09"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0870c09"/><head><date from-iso="+0923-05-18" key="j20583162063308" to-iso="+0937-01-16">後唐</date><placeName key="PL000000042847">鳳翔府</placeName><persName key="A013618">道賢</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0870c10"/><persName key="A013618">釋道賢</persName>，不知何許人也。持諷《孔雀王經》<ptr target="#n3132"/>以<lb
ed="T" n="0870c11"/>為日計，末則受瑜伽灌頂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g97"/>法，持明<ptr type="glossary" target="#g249"/>之功愈<lb
ed="T" n="0870c12"/>多徵應。嘗夜夢佛携<persName key="A013618">賢</persName>行，步步蹈履濃雲，<lb
ed="T" n="0870c13"/>若乘剛<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2034"/>焉。每行不知幾百里，而指之曰：「此<lb
ed="T" n="0870c14"/><placeName key="PL000000048266">摩竭陀國</placeName>，此<placeName key="PL000000048239">占波國</placeName>，<placeName key="PL000000048209">南印度</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000055425">西印度</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000055417">迦濕彌<lb
ed="T" n="0870c15"/>羅</placeName>等國。」且行且記，喜躍不勝。及寤覺，冥解<lb
ed="T" n="0870c16"/><placeName key="PL000000048207">五天</placeName><name>梵</name>音，悉曇語言。時<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>僧到<placeName key="PL000000042847"><anchor xml:id="beg0870sgsz9"/>岐<anchor xml:id="end0870sgsz9"/></placeName>下，<placeName key="PL000000049641">葱嶺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0870c17"/>北諸胡僧往往偽稱<placeName key="PL000000048207">五印</placeName>人，<persName key="A013618">賢</persName>以一接語言，<lb
ed="T" n="0870c18"/>先斥之曰：「汝是某國人。」北戎南<name>梵</name>，無敢<anchor xml:id="beg0870sgsz11"/>紿<anchor xml:id="end0870sgsz11"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1350"/><lb
    ed="T" n="0870c19"/>之。<placeName key="PL000000047360">隴坻</placeName>道俗，皆稟承密藏，號<persName key="A013618">阿闍<anchor xml:id="beg0870sgsz13"/>黎<anchor xml:id="end0870sgsz13"/></persName>也。迨<lb
ed="T" n="0870c20"/><date key="j20618442062184" notAfter-iso="+0933-12-19" notBefore-iso="+0933-01-13"><name>長興</name>末</date>，<persName key="A006576">明宗</persName>晏駕<ptr type="glossary" target="#g756"/>，立<persName key="A006577">從厚</persName>為帝，<placeName key="PL000000042847">鳳翔</placeName><persName key="A006578">清泰</persName>不<lb
ed="T" n="0870c21"/>恭其命，遣<persName key="A013619">王思同</persName>帥師伐之，<persName key="A006578">清泰</persName>乃嬰<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g990"/><lb
ed="T" n="0870c22"/>城自守<ptr target="#n3134"/>。<persName key="A006578">清泰</persName>問<persName key="A013618">賢</persName>曰：「危甚矣，如何？」對曰：「召<lb
ed="T" n="0870c23"/><persName key="A013620">竇八郎</persName>，可逆知勝負也。」<persName key="A006578">清泰</persName>出乘城撫眾，<lb
ed="T" n="0870c24"/>其<persName key="A013620">竇八</persName>介甲持戈來馬前，作迎鬪之狀。跳<lb
ed="T" n="0870c25"/>躍已，解甲投戈而走。<persName key="A013618">賢</persName>曰：「此外敵必降之象<lb
ed="T" n="0870c26"/>也。」果如斯說。<persName key="A006578">清泰</persName>乃擁兵而東，召<persName key="A013618">賢</persName>俱行。<lb
ed="T" n="0870c27"/>入<placeName key="PL000000023638">洛</placeName>，即帝位歟，改元曰<name>清泰</name>。<persName key="A013618">賢</persName>奏曰：「年號<lb
ed="T" n="0870c28"/>不佳，何邪？水『清』『石』見。」至<date key="j20626032062957" notAfter-iso="+0936-01-31" notBefore-iso="+0935-02-11">二年</date>，勅移<placeName key="PL000000003731">并州</placeName><persName key="A006579">晉<lb
ed="T" n="0870c29"/>高祖</persName>為<placeName key="PL000000021661">天平軍</placeName>，乃阻兵自固，潛連<placeName key="PL000000006555">契丹</placeName>，長<pb ed="T" n="0871a" xml:id="T50.2061.0871a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0871a01"/>驅入<placeName key="PL000000023638">洛</placeName>，<persName key="A006578">清泰</persName>自焚<ptr target="#n3135"/>，果「石見」之應矣。<placeName key="PL000000000124">晉</placeName>兵未<lb
ed="T" n="0871a02"/>至，<persName key="A013618">賢</persName>先終于<placeName key="PL000000023638">洛</placeName>，今<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023467 #PL000000023602">兩京</ref>傳大教者，皆法孫<lb
ed="T" n="0871a03"/>之曾、玄矣！<persName key="A013620">竇八郎</persName>者，<placeName key="PL000000042847"><anchor xml:id="beg0871sgsz1"/>岐<anchor xml:id="end0871sgsz1"/></placeName>人也，家且富焉。自荷<lb
ed="T" n="0871a04"/>器鬻水，言語不常，唯散髮披衣狂走，與<persName key="A005931">李<lb
ed="T" n="0871a05"/>順興</persName>相類。或遇牛驢車，必撫掌而笑。迨死，<lb
ed="T" n="0871a06"/>焚之，火聚中盡化金色胡蝶而飛去。或手<lb
ed="T" n="0871a07"/>掬、衣扇行之，歸家供養焉。</p>
